sequenceDiagram
  participant A as Agent A
  participant OB1 as OB1 Agent Memory
  participant B as Agent B
  participant Human as Human reviewer

  A->>OB1: Recall prior attempts and constraints
  A->>A: Triage or implement step
  A->>OB1: Write compact work log
  OB1->>Human: Queue high-impact lessons
  Human->>OB1: Confirm, edit, or evidence-only
  B->>OB1: Recall work log and confirmed constraints
  B->>B: Continue without raw transcript
